OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FMorning low cloud and fog will
OL,6,Fquickly disperse to leave a fine and
OL,7,Fsunny day. Any lingering fog in the
OL,8,FIrish Sea may lap onto some coastal
OL,9,Fstretches at times. Feeling very warm
OL,10,Fin the July sunshine, with light winds.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FA warm and sunny evening.
OL,13,FStaying clear overnight, but the risk
OL,14,Fof some fog rolling back in from the
OL,15,FIrish Sea once more. A warm night for
OL,16,Fmost.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
